1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 25=

4
00:00:17,399 --> 00:00:18,719
More precisely,

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,239
I'm Master Baiyi, the one
you've all been so eager to kill.

6
00:00:22,839 --> 00:00:23,920
You... Murong Xiang!

7
00:00:24,079 --> 00:00:25,280
You're the Martial Arts Alliance Leader,

8
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:25,960
yet you've turned on us

9
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:26,800
and sided with evil.

10
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:29,480
Have you forgotten
what honor and decency mean?

11
00:00:30,399 --> 00:00:31,199
The likes of you

12
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:33,520
have no right to lecture me on either.

13
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:34,320
Back when the Murong family

14
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:37,280
was at its weakest,

15
00:00:37,799 --> 00:00:38,880
your sects seized our ancestral estate,

16
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:40,039
slaughtered my clan,

17
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:42,359
and humiliated us in every way.

18
00:00:42,439 --> 00:00:44,399
Did any of you care about
honor and decency then?

19
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:49,159
Amitabha.

20
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:50,560
Murong Xiang,

21
00:00:50,719 --> 00:00:52,960
I urge you to lay down your blade.

22
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:56,399
Revenge only breeds more revenge.

23
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:57,479
Turn back

24
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:58,600
while you still can.

25
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,000
Shut up!

26
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,000
You bald old hypocrite!

27
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:03,920
No sect is more sanctimonious
than Shaolin.

28
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:06,519
My father once begged Shaolin
on his knees for protection.

29
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,840
Not only did you refuse,

30
00:01:07,959 --> 00:01:09,599
but you also beat him
and drove him away.

31
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,200
And you still have the nerve

32
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,079
to tell me to turn back?

33
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,400
You... You...

34
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,760
Why waste words

35
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,799
on a madman like him?

36
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,400
Let's kill him

37
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,480
and be done with it.

38
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:23,799
Exactly.

39
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:27,959
You think you can kill me?

40
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,719
You don't stand a chance.

41
00:01:29,799 --> 00:01:33,200
This is where you'll all die today.

42
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,680
Sect leaders, fellow martial artists,

43
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,560
we're trapped.

44
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,680
If we want to live,

45
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,280
we fight to the death!

46
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,680
Attack!

47
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,439
All the elite disciples
from the major sects...

48
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,439
They're all dead.

49
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,200
Check for survivors.

50
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,159
Mr. Bai!

51
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:20,120
Over here! Mr. Bai is alive!

52
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:24,400
Mr. Bai!

53
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,439
Where are the sect leaders?

54
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:29,560
Bu...

55
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:33,439
Busi Sea.

56
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,599
Mr. Bai!

57
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,400
There's no time to lose. Let's go.

58
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:54,759
It's the Yehuo Duo.

59
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,159
Brat.

60
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,759
You must be Peng Dasheng.

61
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,080
Where's Master Baiyi?

62
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,879
You want to see Master?

63
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,680
You'll have to get past us first.

64
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,960
We'll handle them.

65
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:17,120
Wherever Master Baiyi goes,

66
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,639
all under heaven bow.

67
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,120
When the Soul-Devouring Dagger
is unleashed,

68
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,319
all paths wither.

69
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:33,000
Today, I become the Martial God.

70
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:37,039
And you're all
key to making that happen.

71
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,120
You should feel honored.

72
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:40,960
Now kneel and die!

73
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,120
Murong Xiang!

74
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,240
You murdered fellow martial artists

75
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,400
and betrayed the martial world.

76
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:52,479
Today, we'll deliver Heaven's justice

77
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,439
and strike you down, fiend!

78
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,639
No!

79
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:41,920
You really think you can take me?

80
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:20,920
Your Tai Chi qi is pure.

81
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,519
Too bad

82
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:30,160
it's just fuel for me.

83
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,560
Murong Xiang!

84
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:59,600
Peng Dasheng, you finally came.

85
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,680
I've been waiting for you.

86
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:03,600
Murong Xiang,

87
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,959
I knew all along you were Master Baiyi.

88
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,399
Before coming here,

89
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,120
I had the Wudu Sect round up

90
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,000
every last man at your manor.

91
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:15,279
Your crimes are already known
throughout the martial world.

92
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,720
That's all right. I don't blame you.

93
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,040
Look at me.

94
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,800
I'm already a demigod.

95
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:26,160
Who in the martial world
would dare refuse

96
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:29,360
to bow at my feet now?

97
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,639
There's one thing
you failed to account for.

98
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,439
The natural barrier caused
by my sealed meridians is gone.

99
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:39,360
And my Formless Sea of Qi

100
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:42,000
has fused with the spiritual power
inside the soul jade.

101
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:45,720
My cultivation
is on a whole new level now.

102
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:46,759
Is that so?

103
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:49,839
Then don't disappoint me.

104
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,040
Murong Xiang,

105
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,800
to feed your ambition,

106
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,360
you used the Demon Sect

107
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,160
to slaughter martial artists

108
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,360
and innocent people.

109
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,560
Today,

110
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,360
I'll make you pay

111
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,879
for what you've done
to the martial world.

112
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,399
Let's see if you've got what it takes.

113
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:15,439
Mountain-Shattering, Sea-Rending Slash!

114
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,839
Not bad.

115
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:24,040
But you're still nowhere near
strong enough to kill me.

116
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,959
Boy, is that all you've got?

117
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,360
To a god,

118
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,279
you're nothing but ants.

119
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,199
Peng Dasheng,

120
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,759
before you die,

121
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,680
let me tell you a secret.

122
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,639
That day,
I had the midwife testify against you

123
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,240
to get you
cast out of the martial world.

124
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,439
It was all to lure

125
00:08:18,439 --> 00:08:21,079
these sect leaders here to die.

126
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,040
And Peng Zhen,
the man from twenty years ago,

127
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,759
really was your father.

128
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,399
Too bad I didn't kill

129
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:33,200
you and your father together back then.

130
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,639
Otherwise, you'd never have gotten
the chance to break Bingqing's heart.

131
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:39,759
Why did you kill my father?

132
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,759
Why did I kill your father?

133
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:44,279
Because he stood in my way.

134
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,440
Years ago,
I seized the Soul-Devouring Dagger

135
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,720
from the former Demon Lord.

136
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:52,200
I discovered it could help me break
through the final barrier to godhood

137
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:54,440
and become a true Martial God.

138
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,080
But when your father found out,

139
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:58,080
he told me to stop.

140
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,159
He knew what I was trying to do,

141
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,919
and he still tried to stop me!

142
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:04,559
Only as a true Martial God

143
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:08,440
could I tear down
the walls between the sects.

144
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:10,519
Without sects,

145
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,200
there'd be no more fighting,

146
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:14,919
and the martial world
could finally know lasting peace.

147
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,960
But he just wouldn't listen.

148
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:19,200
He said I'd lost myself to evil.

149
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:22,039
He said he'd rally
the entire martial world to stop me.

150
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,679
I wounded him in a rage,

151
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,000
but he still got away.

152
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:45,159
Murong Xiang, the child is innocent.

153
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,919
Spare him,

154
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,039
and I'll give you my life.

155
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:50,919
You chose this path yourself.

156
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:59,240
You've already been struck
by my Soul-Devouring Palm.

157
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,960
You and your son will both die here.

158
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,159
You're despicable!

159
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:05,039
I'll kill you!

160
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,879
Xuanzhen!

161
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:12,360
Why are you here?

162
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,519
Stay out of this, you meddling Daoist!

163
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,440
Xuanzhen!

164
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,840
Take the child back to our sect. Hurry!

165
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:20,080
What about you?

166
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:21,840
Today, he and I

167
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,720
settle our score.

168
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,759
I've turned all my cultivation

169
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:29,919
into spiritual power
and poured it into this jade.

170
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,320
If this child grows up,

171
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:35,600
this may help him someday.

172
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,039
All right.

173
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:41,919
I promise I'll raise him.

174
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:50,600
Murong Xiang, I'll give you my life.

175
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:52,240
We were friends once.

176
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:54,080
Let our grudges end with me.

177
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,279
My Soul-Devouring Technique

178
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:12,799
didn't kill you that day,

179
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:15,279
but it did leave you
with sealed meridians.

180
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:18,279
I thought you wouldn't live long.

181
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:20,200
But that meddling Daoist

182
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,519
somehow kept you alive

183
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:23,679
all these years.

184
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,279
So,

185
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,600
everyone was just a pawn to you,

186
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:32,279
even your own daughter?

187
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,879
I planned for everything,

188
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,279
but I never expected

189
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:40,200
that old fox, your master,

190
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:43,279
to arrange your engagement to Bingqing.

191
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,559
But at this point,

192
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:46,519
none of that matters.

193
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:49,360
You've witnessed my rise to godhood

194
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,320
in your father's place.

195
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:54,360
Now it's time to send you to join him.

196
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:21,700
♪Come on♪

197
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:26,900
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

198
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:31,820
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

199
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:35,020
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

200
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:38,100
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

201
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:41,100
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

202
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:44,580
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

203
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:47,820
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

204
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:50,900
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

205
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:53,820
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

206
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:57,700
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

207
00:12:57,740 --> 00:13:00,740
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

208
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:06,420
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

209
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:08,860
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

210
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:11,940
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

211
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:15,060
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

212
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:18,860
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

213
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:21,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

214
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,620
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

215
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:28,060
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

216
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:32,380
♪I am my own king♪

217
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:47,020
♪I emerge into the world♪

218
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:48,780
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

219
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:50,140
♪My pride is my trump card♪

220
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,940
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

221
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,340
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

222
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:55,100
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

223
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,620
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

224
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:58,340
♪I dare to break every rule♪

225
00:13:58,340 --> 00:13:59,660
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

226
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:01,500
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

227
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:02,740
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

228
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:04,980
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

229
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,500
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

230
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:08,100
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

231
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,700
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

232
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,420
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

233
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:13,140
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

234
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:14,500
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

235
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:16,140
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

236
00:14:16,140 --> 00:14:17,620
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

237
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:19,340
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

238
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:20,940
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

239
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:22,500
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

240
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:26,820
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

241
00:14:26,820 --> 00:14:28,980
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

242
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:31,580
♪Let me write the legend♪

243
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:39,020
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

244
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:42,340
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

245
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:44,820
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

246
00:14:44,820 --> 00:14:48,900
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

247
00:14:49,260 --> 00:14:51,860
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

248
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:54,340
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

249
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:57,380
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

250
00:14:57,380 --> 00:15:02,420
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
